/*
Key Commands:
<Up,Dn Arrows> : select widget focus. PgUp,PgDn hop by 5 entries.
<Lt,Rt Arrows> : alter value of focused widget
<0>   : focused value -> 0.0
<E>   : animate just focused value (A,Z affect amount)
<X>   : toggle animation
<Spc> : reset
<1>...<7> to load preset images

Drag mouse on X axis to alter focused widget value.
Note: mouse X affects focused value, mouse Y affects next entry

Accelerated changes while holding down arrow keys or moving the mouse:
Hold down <A> for change Amount * 0.1
Hold down <Z> for change Amount * 10.
Hold down both <A><Z> for change Amount * 50.

Shape design:           https://fractalforums.org/programming/11/mango/5159/msg37976#new
Coloring:               https://www.shadertoy.com/view/NdXBzr
Distance functions:     https://iquilezles.org/articles/distfunctions2d/
Text display:           https://www.shadertoy.com/view/mdsSD7
Keyboard:               https://www.shadertoy.com/view/lsXGzf
Javascript rendition:   https://openprocessing.org/sketch/1964673

*/

